==================================================
1. MAIN DESCRIPTION OF THE PROGRAM
==================================================

This program is a password-protected paper-trading research and execution dashboard for U.S. swing trades.

The strategy combines:
- momentum from daily price action
- sentiment from recent news
- earnings surprise from reported versus estimated EPS
- earnings-call transcript tone from Alpha Vantage

The current app supports:
- manual paper trading through Alpaca
- a live signal dashboard
- a backtester with realistic friction assumptions
- a walk-forward research lab for parameter stability
- a paper-trade journal with factor attribution
- a market regime filter based on SPY trend and breadth

Current design constraints:
- long-only
- swing trading
- paper trading first
- auto-trading off by default
- free/cheap data aware
- understandable before clever

